Documents
---------
See:
	generalserver/config/websites/general_server/
		TODO.xml
		WHY.xml
		README.xml

Server Control
--------------
In
	generalserver/
Run
	bin/generalserver
This, by default, loads the XML tree from
	./config
Which contains the overall setup: services, databases, etc.

Installation
------------
cd src/
./configure
make
make install

Debugging
---------
cd src
./configure --with-debug
make
make install
gdb bin/generalserver
